summary: Allows fast travel from interior cells in Skyrim, Dawnguard and Dragonborn to exterior cells via the fast travel mode.
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/jMmBy9e.jpg?2[/IMG]
SIMPLE WORLDWIDE INTERIOR FAST TRAVEL- S.W.I.F.T.

I made this mod for myself since the mod that I was using did not cover Dawnguard and Dragonborn locations and the one that did had extraneous master files. Quite simply this mod allows you to travel from any interior cell in Skyrim or Solstien to any exterior cell via the fast travel mode. There are certain intentional exclusions because fast travel from these locations might break the quest involved. The only change to any interior cell is the ability to fast travel.This is designed as a convenience mod to bypass multiple loading screens.

EXCLUDED LOCATIONS

Azura’s Star Interior
Cidna Mine
Markarth Ruins
Obscured Passage
Dimhollow Crypt
Dimhollow Cavern
Inner Sanctum-Forgotten Vale
Runvald Temple
Apocrypha-ALL
Temple of Mirak Sanctum
Dustman’s Crypt
Helgan Keep
Japhet’s Folly Tower
Irkanghan Sanctuary
Thalmor HQ & Embassy
Soul Cairn
All Hold’s Player Holding Cells

_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
FILE REQUIREMENTS:
Skyrim
Dawnguard
Dragonborn
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
THIS MOD SINCE IT AFFECTS SO MANY CELLS NEEDS TO BE AS CLOSE TO THE BOTTOM OF YOUR LOAD ORDER AS POSSIBLE, PREFERABLY LAST.
It will not work on new cells created by other authors.
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

It has been playtested with Skyrim V-1.9.32.08, Dawnguard DLC and Dragonborn DLC, it works with or without SKSE.
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

My thanks to my playtestors Grannywills & Roguespear who graciously volunteered to be my coal mine canaries.
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
I EXPRESSLY FORBID THE RE-UPLOADING OF THIS MOD TO ANY OTHER SITE. I RETAIN ALL AUTHORSHIP PREROGATIVES.
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
